OL,3,GBLOOPERSCBBC One Scotland broadcasts
OL,4,CThe One Show studio output in error
OL,5,
OL,6,FViewers of BBC One Scotland were
OL,7,Funexpectedly presented with output from
OL,8,FThe One Show studio during the opening
OL,9,Fminutes of tonight's BBC News at Six.
OL,11,FSeconds into the opening titles for the
OL,12,FBBC News at Six ` and after the opening
OL,13,Fnetwork and Scottish headlines ` The
OL,14,FOne Show studio was put to air.
OL,16,FPresenters Clara Amfo and Alex Jones
OL,17,Fwere seen and heard chatting with
OL,18,Fmembers of the programme's production
OL,19,Fteam.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,151,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15002
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F150A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCBBC One Scotland broadcasts
OL,4,CThe One Show studio output in error
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe presenters were also seen having a
OL,7,Fpromotional photo taken and recording a
OL,8,Fshort video for social media ahead of
OL,9,Ftonight's live show.
OL,11,FThe BBC News at Six was put back on air
OL,12,F` with over two-and-a-half minutes of
OL,13,Fthe programme missed.
OL,15,FA separate issue affected the link into
OL,16,Ftonight's 6pm news across all BBC One
OL,17,Fnations and regions.
OL,19,FThere seemed to be a timing discrepancy
OL,20,Fbetween the link into the BBC News at
OL,21,FSix and when the programme itself
OL,22,Fstarted.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,151,140,200,120,0,100
