OL,3,GBLOOPERSCBBC One Scotland broadcasts
OL,4,CThe One Show studio output in error
OL,5,
OL,6,FOn Network BBC One (and English
OL,7,Fregions) we joined the BBC News at Six
OL,8,Fa few seconds late, with presenter
OL,9,FSophie Raworth already reading out the
OL,10,Fopening headline.
OL,12,FOn BBC One Northern Ireland, the
OL,13,Fopening of the Six is taken off the
OL,14,Fclean feed of BBC One, which was still
OL,15,Fon the BBC blocks loop (played between
OL,16,Fprogrammes on the clean feed) when
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland cut to it.
OL,19,FWe then saw just shy of 10 seconds of
OL,20,Flive output from The One Show studio,
OL,21,Fbefore cutting back to the BBC News at
OL,22,FSix.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
