OL,3,GBLOOPERSCBBC One Scotland broadcasts
OL,4,CThe One Show studio output in error
OL,5,
OL,6,FBBC One Scotland and BBC One Wales
OL,7,Fappeared to take a dirty feed of
OL,8,FNetwork BBC One, and caught a few
OL,9,Fseconds of the Network BBC One ident.
